item Food Safety

  Food Safety In General; Multiple Topics

     * Frequently Asked Questions About Food Safety from the USDA Meat and
       Poultry Hotline
       Questions are arranged in the following categories:
          + Food Storage, Preparation and Handling
          + Bacteria, Spoilage
          + Foodborne Illness
          + Product Recalls
          + Meat and Poultry Inspection, and Other FSIS Programs
          + Labeling, Dating, Food Additives
          + Natural Flavorings on Meat and Poultry Labels
          + Cookware and Equipment
          + Nutrition
     * Frequently Asked Questions for Consumers, Business & Industry
       www.FoodSafety.gov, Gateway to Government Food Safety Information
       [Exiting this site]
       (Indexes more than 500 questions on a host of topics!)
